Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.87,0:00:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類背負著原罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.74,0:00:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慾望就像原罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.08,0:00:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在原罪上釘著十字架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.01,0:00:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在慾望之下尋來著留名野史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.36,0:00:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如在九澄醫院工作的女人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.63,0:01:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有那些男人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.18,0:01:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄春旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.31,0:01:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄醫院院長的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.32,0:01:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今卻只和母親一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.13,0:01:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親死後就以父親九澄春慶 兒子的名義在醫院過活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.61,0:01:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在來到醫院之前完全不了解 新爸爸的事情的春旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.82,0:01:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然背負著原罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.15,0:01:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵圍宏子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.62,0:01:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄醫院的護士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在極美的外表之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.09,0:02:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承著原罪 而被慾望吞噬的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.83,0:02:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北富恭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.50,0:02:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄醫院的護士長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在院長面前是絕對的服從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被慾望所困淫蕩的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄春慶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄醫院的院長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.05,0:02:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為春旗的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.12,0:02:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟女人廝混來祭祀慾望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻庭亞由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄醫院的護士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的外表之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.27,0:02:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏著自己的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.08,0:02:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個謎樣的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被慾望所擒獲的男人和女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.95,0:03:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深陷在原罪的漩渦裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.14,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且追尋著光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.36,0:04:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能從原罪的數量以及 被原罪所束縛裡所掙脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.30,0:04:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是被這個男人害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個賤貨 代替妳的媽媽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.65,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的母親跟別人跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.78,0:04:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也跟她是同種女人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的很好唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.85,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳 小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.20,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.36,0:05:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我把我的父親….)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 九澄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是亞由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.40,0:05:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.07,0:05:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由美 恭喜妳合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白衣很適合妳 而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.14,0:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟母親一模一樣是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.95,0:06:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我想去拜訪你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.62,0:06:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我完成心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.16,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳 我明天要去德國了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻庭的事我聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.17,0:06:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去德國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.24,0:06:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是已經接受我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次讓我們兩人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春慶先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.85,0:06:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中也非常喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.98,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也想我們兩人一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.00,0:07:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙把媽媽從我身邊搶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人的原罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要補償了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是亞由美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.04,0:07:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚還在值班 真辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由美也一起來怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 宏子這麼的高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊也很喜歡做愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也沒抱怨什麼 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了啊 亞由美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了啊 亞由美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.56,0:08:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗君 已經夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的話 就去房間做好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.30,0:08:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那樣就沒意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.31,0:08:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.22,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經去了 真不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒爽夠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡亂搞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.10,0:09:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是無法阻止那個女人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了自己的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.39,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被爸爸給抱了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.27,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北富小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.03,0:10:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有比這個更刺激的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.78,0:10:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然搞了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是即使用了道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.11,0:10:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎還不是很爽的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要凡士林對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.99,0:10:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 春旗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.26,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要用那種東西的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.19,0:10:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用在我身體裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不趕快舔的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.91,0:11:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要用凡士林囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以插進來了 春旗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 插入吧 春旗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.87,0:12:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說的話 我就早點插吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射出來 射出來也可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.07,0:13:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂生存的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.54,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是累積在一個個的罪行上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則人是無法生存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.68,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是一個小小的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有繼承罪行這條路而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.35,0:13:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由美 我出身就是為了要 承續這些罪行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著妳 背負著妳母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.56,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想妳們是不會原諒我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.04,0:13:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還想多等一會兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.32,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有一個人原諒了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊 亞由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他完成他的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有這個權利 不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是讓妳知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 妳也就滿足了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.35,0:14:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親還是沒有完成他的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣過逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.26,0:15:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院每天還是一樣的過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.76,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這個醫院為首的全部財產 就留給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你也可以長住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成自己的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.97,0:16:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼自己的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.18,0:16:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院長很重視身為兒子的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定認為身為醫院的院長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒發現自己的病情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸早就知道自己要死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓我繼承醫院是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.59,0:16:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己尋找答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼爸爸要我繼承呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親死之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.48,0:16:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道爸爸的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.41,0:16:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以做哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.98,0:17:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以那樣做過份的事 也可以唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.79,0:17:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不會討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.26,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直可以把我當做對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從亞由美那裡聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.07,0:17:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還恨院長嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家都不恨院長哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.41,0:17:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟在這住院的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.02,0:17:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧身體洗乾淨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞的話是洗不乾淨的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.63,0:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會撒嬌的孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.37,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個非常可愛的小男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.65,0:18:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的醫院都不願意接受他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.92,0:18:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是院長卻願意治療我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.53,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而北富小姐也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.81,0:18:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前被不良份子給輪姦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被輪姦的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.51,0:19:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著孩子想自盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.25,0:19:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 拯救她的是院長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.13,0:19:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家沒有人是恨院長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是感謝他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.47,0:20:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拯救了 一個一個背負著原罪的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.02,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要打起精神哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.43,0:20:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來事情是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.24,0:20:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親背負著大家的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.72,0:20:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這樣好不習慣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.38,0:21:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗 拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.78,0:21:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡 那裡好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.48,0:21:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦 這麼的溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.48,0:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.28,0:21:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丟臉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.42,0:21:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要春旗君的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.76,0:22:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.03,0:22:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.77,0:22:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏子 妳是這麼的可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再深 再深一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再深一點 春旗君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.25,0:23:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.82,0:24:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了爸爸所說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.23,0:24:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要走自己的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.23,0:24:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要做些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.03,0:24:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要承續父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.77,0:24:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續背負著她們的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.77,0:24:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都要背負著原罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.52,0:24:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽 我會遵守和父親的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.00,0:24:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.07,0:24:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在醫院打算做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.27,0:24:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和春旗約定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.07,0:24:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直和他在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.81,0:25:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳弟弟的事打算怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.01,0:25:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春旗是不能代替妳弟弟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.35,0:25:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.36,0:25:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.43,0:25:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在在休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.64,0:25:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她懷孕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.77,0:25:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷孕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.51,0:25:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續背負原罪的他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.85,0:25:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法從原罪中逃脫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.93,0:25:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇終
